      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it doesn't matter what they think though. because even when they aren't looking, i feel like i'm just a mistake. like i'm taking up space that someone better should be using. everything i try to do just makes it worse and the more i try to fix things, the more people just pile on. it feels like there's no version of the future where this actually gets better. it just feels like a loop of being hated.",
